org.letras.util.region.document
Class RegionImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.mundo.rt.Service
      org.letras.util.region.document.RegionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRegion, org.mundo.rt.IEmits
public class RegionImpl
extends org.mundo.rt.Service
implements IRegion

Default IRegion implementation. Clients can use this for publishing regions. Publishing a region is achieved by calling Mundo.registerService(Service) on an instance of this class.

Just instantiating a RegionImpl is not enough to receive events and samples. See RegionAdapterFactory and RegionAdapter for this.

Author:
jannik
